pleteness relation. With this extra treatment\nto ensure the integrals are dual conformally invariant, each Mondrian diagram\ncan be exactly translated to its corresponding physical loop integrand after\nbeing summed over all ordered subspaces that admit it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Dec 2017 18:54:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 11:14:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 20 Jun 2018 17:08:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-21"}
