3\\rm\\,pc$, only in a dense\nenvironment with $n_{ism}\\geq\\rm1\\,cm^{-3}$. The requirement of the dense\nsurrounding gas is supported by the presence of molecular clouds found in the\nsource vicinity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Dec 2017 09:47:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 03:17:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
